{"tid":2266691,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"《鬼滅之刃》熱度持續燃燒！ 日本上映16天觀影人次破千萬","createTime":"2020-11-01T13:29:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T16:04:14.000Z","uid":314004,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3600ddbdae65af892e6ae40d814ce6587cef550c","tid":2266691,"uid":314004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T13:29:50.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕超高人氣的日本漫畫《鬼滅之刃》，其劇場版《鬼滅之刃劇場版 無限列車篇》上月16日在日本上映後頻頻刷新日本電影票房紀錄，不但上映短短10天後票房就突破100億日圓，<strong>在上映16天總觀影人次更突破了1000萬人次，遠遠打破《你的名字》的39天破千萬觀影人次成績。</strong><br />\n<br />\n綜合日媒報導，《鬼滅之刃劇場版》上映引爆日本鬼滅熱潮，短短10天後票房就突破100億日圓，超越《神隱少女》25天、《你的名字》28天破百億票房紀錄，官方昨（31日）也宣布，《鬼滅之刃》上映16天總觀影人次突破了1000萬人次。<br />\n<br />\n票房統計推特估計，<strong>《鬼滅之刃劇場版 無限列車篇》上映16天累計票房約143.3億，超越新海誠《天氣之子》141.9億、迪士尼動畫《冰雪奇緣2》等巨作，來到日本歷年票房紀錄第12名</strong>，是否能挑戰《神隱少女》308億日本票房紀錄成為網路熱門挑論話題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3338391\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3338391&d=Xh6WvVyDZ%2Fzj0BED8lYnhxPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=220174ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3338391&h=5e8a5c49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3338391</a>"},{"pid":"436580dc20d4bbfb60b8270dcc22daeb3a098909","tid":2266691,"uid":299548,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T13:45:20.000Z","msg":"鬼滅的確好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n早排睇fsn hf電影 一開頭播幾分鐘鬼滅PV已經哭能左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aphaSRr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Faph